Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:29.25,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\pos(490,518)}Tradução: Crunchyroll \NTranscrição Juan Tlgd \NRevisão: RAFAEL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:37.72,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\pos(514,530)}Initial timing\N{\fs40}Kuzan @ Vegapunk Fansubs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:41.43,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\pos(514,500)}Timing\N{\fs40}Galaxy 9000
